products.title: Dining table
products.description: The plank look, created with a top layer of oak, enhances the crafted, farmhouse expression. Every table is unique with varying grain patterns and natural color shifts. A robust table ready to entertain. The table has a full plank design that gives it an authentic plank expression with a genuine wood feeling. The plank expression is enhanced by the design on the edges. This table has been tested against our strictest standards for stability, durability and safety to withstand everyday use in your home for years.
